new.name: CVE-2024-31210
new.description: This Ruby script checks if a given WordPress site is vulnerable to CVE-2024-31210, which allows administrator-level users on single-site installations and Super Admin-level users on Multisite installations to execute arbitrary PHP code via the plugin upload mechanism.
